\family sans
"sense"
\family default
 strand and the string 
\family sans
aseq
\family default
 becomes the 
\family sans
"anti"
\family default
 strand.
 
\family sans
seq
\family default
 and 
\family sans
aseq
\family default
 are required to be complementary although this is not checked.
 
\family sans
wc_helix()
\family default
